{{wikipedia}}
==English==

===Noun===
'''thrush'''  (''plural'' '''thrushes''')
# One of several species of [[songbird]]s of the family ''[[Turdidae]]'', often with spotted underbellies such as the [[bluebird]], [[nightingale]], and [[robin]].
# {{pathology}} The common name for the fungal infection [[candidiasis]].
# ''(slang)'' A woman who sings popular songs.

